data.description: This Mocksville home has the amount of room you need to spread out and enjoy your own space. You can use the mostly finished basement as an in-law suite since there is a bonus room with a fireplace, 4th bedroom and a full bath. Bonus room ceiling height less than 7 ft. Sitting on a nice .75 acre lot with an aesthetically pleasing wooded backyard view, this property has a good template for some updating. Carpeting needs replacement and the microwave above the stove is not operating. Rear deck needs some repair. Dishwasher was replaced approximately 4 months ago. HVAC unit has some age on it. Roof age is unknown. Stainless refrigerator does convey. Washer/dryer will not convey. Basement workshop has a work bench & shelving. Several holes in two walls. Leak in a bathroom has caused some damage to bathroom flooring and ceiling in basement. Sale will need to be court approved. This home just needs some fresh touches and with the overall living space, this is a hidden gem!
